criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age > 18 years;

          -  Di-chorionic (DC)or Mono-chorionic (MC) twin pregnancies;

          -  Both live fetuses at 11+0-13+6 weeks of gestation;

          -  Informed and written consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Monoamniotic twins

          -  Triplet pregnancies that had undergone embryo reduction to twins or with one vanishing
             twin

          -  Women who are unconscious or severely ill, those with learning difficulties, or
             serious mental illness;

          -  Any other reason the clinical investigators think will prevent the potential
             participant from complying with the trial protocol.
